Package io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.checkbox

Class CheckboxServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.base.AbstractComponentService<CheckboxComponentType,Checkbox>
io.cyborgcode.roa.ui.components.checkbox.CheckboxServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
CheckboxService, Insertion
public class CheckboxServiceImpl extends AbstractComponentService<CheckboxComponentType,Checkbox> implements CheckboxService
Provides service-level operations for interacting with checkbox components.

This class handles selection, deselection, verification of states (selected/enabled), and retrieval of checkbox values, delegating the interactions to appropriate Checkbox implementations based on the given CheckboxComponentType.
